{"tid":837581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020東京奧運有無巴絲報名做義工?","createTime":"2018-09-26T13:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T15:55:54.000Z","uid":88102,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"498c2ecb2c8a16a8ccf71b66f52e97f60cf33dfb","tid":837581,"uid":88102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tokyo2020.org/jp/special/volunteer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftokyo2020.org%2Fjp%2Fspecial%2Fvolunteer%2F&d=OgkHSPCzxhFKAGDEGozo1f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5c820507\" target=\"_blank\">https://tokyo2020.org/jp/special/volunteer/</a><br />\n今日開始報名啦,日期去到12月頭,但無分先後次序<br />\n如果係日本留緊學就更加唔好錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我當初都以為海外唔報得,但照佢咁講,觀光VISA都應該得<br />\n有無巴絲知道詳細係點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQ : Does &lsquo;residency qualification to stay in Japan&rsquo; mean that I will be required to obtain a long-term visa?<br />\n<br />\nA : 'Residency qualification to stay in Japan' is a residency qualification that allows holders to stay in Japan legally. Short-term stay visas are also included in these qualifications."},{"pid":"6e1eb9340d44288c40cf3fedcf332b4b719dd48d","tid":837581,"uid":88102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d90da0708a053e018bb2f5bc6de9808adb1ce0","tid":837581,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"你去唔去得曬d面試/訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d89a4adfad5687767915b7c617a9b71cf7b3d5","tid":837581,"uid":101909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:19:04.000Z","msg":"自己比住，應該貴到喊"},{"pid":"ea2224e22d57f5b422d3af94d19191b5323a4552","tid":837581,"uid":50779,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"repl